      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The New Haven Oratorio Society Papers document the Society's activities. The Papers include minutes and records of meetings, subscription records, programs, and financial records.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <bioghist id="aspace_bh1">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The New Haven Oratorio Society was founded on October 1, 1903, under Horatio Parker, Dean of the Yale School of Music. The Society gave its last concert in 1913.</p>  
      </bioghist>
